                <head>233. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>During the North Atlantic Council Ministerial meeting at Bonn, May 2–4, the
                    Foreign Ministers discussed a paper entitled “The Satellites” (<gloss
                        target="#t_NATO1">NATO</gloss> document C–M(57)57), which, among other
                    things, reviewed the reaction of the North Atlantic Treaty Organization to
                    serious complications in the German Democratic Republic. Regarding this <gloss
                        target="#t_NAC1">NAC</gloss> session, see <ref
                        target="frus1955-57v04#pg_167">volume IV, pages 167</ref>–<ref
                        target="frus1955-57v04#pg_169">169</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
